FEATURES
-  Request for cleaning
    -  Cleaning Completed confirmation
    -  Feedback from student after cleaning
    -  Tip for employee
    -  Complain related to Room or Bathrooms
    -  Lost and Found
-  Complaints
-  Food Request
-  Leave Application
-  Maintenance Request
-  Online Noticeboard
-  Web socket connection


AUTHENTICATION
  - Login
    -  Single Login for both Students and Employees (Managed under backend)
    -  Student Login : Login with VIT ID and Password
    -  Employee Login : Login with Email ID or Mobile No and OTP or Password
    -  Moderator Login : Login with Email ID and Password

  - SignUp
    -  Register as an employee
      - Register with email id
      - Register with mobile no
    -  Register as a student

  Register as a STUDENT
  - Name and Gender (Dropdown)
  - Reg No
  - Block Name (Deopdown) and Room No
  - VIT email id
  - Password
  - Confirm Password

  Register as an Employee
  - Name
  - Emp ID
  - Block Assosciated
  - Email id
  - Password
  - Confirm Password


Architecture
- Student
  - Name
  - Reg No
  - Gender
  - Block Name
  - Room No
  - VIT Email
  - Password
  
- Employee
  - Name
  - Emp ID
  - Email ID
  - Block Associated
  - Password
